Privacy Policy.
Last updated: 1 july 2024.
1. Introduction
Welcome to Video Logo maker! This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and safeguard your personal information when you use our logo maker iOS app. By using the app, you agree to the practices described in this Privacy Policy.
2.Information We Collect
2.1 Personal Information.
We may collect the following personal information when you use our app:
- Your name and contact information (such as email address) when you provide it voluntarily.
- User-generated content, including logos and designs you create using our app.
- Usage and device information, including but not limited to device type, operating system, and app usage patterns.
2.2 Non-Personal Information
We may also collect non-personal information, such as anonymized usage statistics and data that does not directly identify you.
3. How We Use Your Information
We use your personal information for the following purposes:
- To provide and improve our logo maker services.
- To communicate with you, respond to your inquiries, and provide customer support.
- To send you updates, newsletters, and marketing materials (if you have opted in).
- To analyze app usage and trends to enhance user experience
- To comply with legal obligations and protect our rights.
4. Data Security
We take reasonable steps to protect your personal information from unauthorized access or disclosure. However, no data transmission over the internet can be guaranteed as 100% secure, so we cannot guarantee the security of your information.
5. Data Deletion
You have the right to request the deletion of your personal information from our systems. To do so, please contact us at
appdev350@protool.app
Our app allows you to save drafts of your logos, business cards, and videos for future editing and use. These drafts are stored locally within our app. All data will be deleted when you delete the app.
6. Third-Party Services
Our app may contain links to third-party websites or services. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these third parties, and we encourage you to review their privacy policies.
7. Children's Privacy
Our app is not intended for use by individuals under the age of 13. We do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13. If you are a parent or guardian and believe we have collected information about your child, please contact us, and we will delete the information.
8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices and legal requirements. We will notify you of any material changes by posting the updated Privacy Policy within the app.
9. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about our Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
appdev350@protool.app